config VIDEO_IMX135
        tristate "IMX135 camera sensor support"
        depends on I2C && ARCH_TEGRA
        ---help---
          This is a driver for the IMX135 camera sensor
          for use with the tegra isp.  The sensor has a
          maximum of 13MP (4208x3120) resolution with HDR
          capability.

