config VIDEO_OV7695
        tristate "OV7695 camera sensor support"
        depends on I2C && ARCH_TEGRA
        ---help---
          This is a driver for the OV7695 YUV camera sensor device
          This sensor has external ISP, it isn't using tegra ISP.

